title: Average Risk Assessments of Polling Locations by District, Eastern District of Afghanistan, 2009 Presidential Election
name: Average Risk Assessments of Polling Locations by District, Eastern District of Afghanistan, 2009 Presidential Election
description:
This dataset displays average data on the security risk assessments of polling locations throughout districts in Eastern Afghanistan. The included districts are from the provinces of Kunar, Laghman, Nangarhar, and Nuristan.

Data with a reading of unk means that data was unknown for that field.

The threat level is on a level of 1 to 3. 1 = low, 2 = medium, 3 = high.

The data has been provided by Todd Huffman.
